text: Acalypha raivavensis is a species of plant in the family Euphorbiaceae. It is endemic to French Polynesia. ==See also== *Flora of Tubuai ==Sources== * raivavensis Category:Flora of the Tubuai Islands Category:Critically endangered flora of Oceania Category:Taxonomy articles created by Polbot Category:Plants described in 1935
title: Acalypha raivavensis
